*"Profesore, da li ste spremni za predavanje?" (Professor, are you ready for the lecture?)

*"Profesore, da li možemo ponovo da prođemo kroz materiju?" (Professor, can we go over the material again?)

*"Profesorima smo dali najviše poštovanje." (We gave the professors the highest respect.)

*"Profesorima je pružena prilika da se izjasne o tome." (Professors were given the opportunity to express their opinion on this.)

*"Moj profesor je rekao da je to bio dobar odgovor." (My professor said that was a good answer.)